{"tid":2346240,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pixel 5、4a 5G 超廣角相機的天文攝影模式被取消了","createTime":"2020-12-30T06:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T06:02:32.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da339d56c2d5c857b49151a47c5a9079d030a373","tid":2346240,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/70414030-4a47-11eb-bbd6-9ccfafbf6373\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F70414030-4a47-11eb-bbd6-9ccfafbf6373&h=3b783b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPixel 5 和 Pixel 4a 5G 的雙主相機由廣角相機和超廣角相機組成，在剛推出時還以兩個相機均可拍攝星夜的天文攝影模式為賣點。但在 11 月更新包推出之後，突然就發現超廣角相機不能再進入天文攝影模式，就只有廣角相機能用。Google 方面沒有主動交代事情，但在天文攝影模式的支援頁面中，就發現有多加一句話，就是在「Pixel 4a 5G 和 Pixel 5 上的天文攝影模式，只能在縮放度等於或大於 1x」，變相就是確認了超廣角相機不能用了。<br />\n<br />\n目前未知 Google 為什麼會有如此改動，但 Gizmodo 就指出，這可能與超廣角相機的成像不穩定有關。因為在 Pixel 手機社群裡就有一些用戶回報指出，超廣角相機在用天文攝影模式拍攝得出的成像，會有明顯的泛綠問題，同時也有大量數位雜訊，與廣角相機得出來的乾淨完美成像，成了極大落差。但畢竟城市人都沒幾次機會能拍到星空了，所以似乎都沒有太多人受影響（吧？）。不過我們仍然有向 Google 查詢事件，希望得到解答。"},{"pid":"66d2313128231bada34c3bd52acdc6c77b0b35a3","tid":2346240,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/google-removes-pixel-5-4a-5g-astrophotography-mode-023729023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fgoogle-removes-pixel-5-4a-5g-astrophotography-mode-023729023.html&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e22c1249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/google-removes-pixel-5-4a-5g-astrophotography-mode-023729023.html</a>"},{"pid":"2dee963ebed2b8eadd87d4fcf3fee93221cf8ce3","tid":2346240,"uid":341649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"星空唔用超廣角不如唔好影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Google好嘢"},{"pid":"c2f4a89b43e8db5accab7b11aa983c3030da6e5b","tid":2346240,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}